content: Only once you have made sure all the Wasp Guai are gone from the edges should you hop into the pit itself, and take out the Amourworms to reach the very far side, where your reward will be in the form of a **Treasure Chest** that should hold a Gold Tree Core and other materials.

This is an excerpt from the file 'Webbed_Hollow-Lower_Hollow_Walkthrough.md', within the main section titled 'Webbed Hollow - Lower Hollow Walkthrough', specifically from the subsection 'Lower Hollow'.
The content is as follows:
Only once you have made sure all the Wasp Guai are gone from the edges should you hop into the pit itself, and take out the Amourworms to reach the very far side, where your reward will be in the form of a **Treasure Chest** that should hold a Gold Tree Core and other materials.
